[Teleport to Hunting Grounds]
You may teleport to any of the following hunting locations. Each teleport requires a sum of AA.
Necropolis of Sacrifice (20-30) - 29000 AA
Pilgrim's Necropolis (30-40) - 32000 AA
Necropolis of Worship (40-50) - 38000 AA
Patriot's Necropolis (50-60) - 49000 AA

Catacomb of the Heretic (30-40) - 34000 AA
Catacomb of the Branded (40-50) - 50000 AA
Catacomb of the Apostate (50-60) - 44000 AA
